@subsection Ignoring Blocks üôÖ

Use the @samp{:eval} parameter to prevent evaluation of blocks that aren't for your presentation.
@example
#+begin_src elisp :eval never
  (message "Who cares?  I am never evaluated")
#+end_src
@end example

